RODIMUS smiled down at NIGHTLIGHT as he shifted to his robotic form
and landed carrying NIGHTLIGHT in his arms. &quot;Yes it is truely me.&quot;

RODIMUS landed at the entrance to the ARK as he watched the others
make their way back. RODIMUS stood much taller and broader than
before, his robot mode having changed almost as much as his beastmode
had done. He now stood at nearly 15 feet tall and looked much
different than before.

The dark figure of LEGACY walked up to RODIMUS, &quot;I can see that you
have underwent changes.&quot; He said in cold factual tones.

RODIMUS smiled grimly at LEGACY, &quot;More than you know.&quot; He looked at
the other MAXIMALS as they came in but kept his voice low, pitched
just for LEGACY to hear, although it is possible that NIGHTLIGHT might
near it too. &quot;We will need to speak when this is over. You and some of
the others.&quot;

LEGACY nodded, &quot;I had expected as much.&quot;

Turning back to NIGHTLIGHT there was a smile from RODIMUS, &quot;I have
seen the MATRIX, and it tells me that there are more changes coming.&quot;
He said grimly both to LEGACY ads well as NIGHTLIGHT.

LEGACY nodded, &quot;You have passed beyond my knowledge of the future to
be of assistance.&quot; The dark figure said, a hint of sadness in his cold
tones. &quot;But what little I know confirms that something is on the
horizon.&quot;

